function [rmse_by_int, rmse_by_class] = my_rmse(desired, predicted)
square_error = (desired - predicted).^2;
trial_starts = find(diff(any(desired, 2)) > 0);
trial_stops = find(diff(any(desired, 2)) < 0);
RMSE = -1*ones(length(trial_starts),2);% initialize variable
for i=1:1:length(trial_starts)
SE_window = square_error(trial_starts(i):trial_stops(i),:);
RMSE(i,:) = sqrt(sum(SE_window)./length(SE_window));
end
RMSE_ordered = RMSE;
for i=2:2:length(RMSE)
RMSE_ordered(i,[1 2]) = RMSE_ordered(i,[2 1]);
end
rmse_by_int = RMSE_ordered;
rmse_by_class = RMSE;
end
 
function [idx_start, idx_stop] = get_trial_idxs(desired, trial_number)
trial_starts = find(diff(any(desired, 2)) > 0);
trial_stops = find(diff(any(desired, 2)) < 0);
idx_start = trial_starts(trial_number);
idx_stop = trial_stops(trial_number+1);
end
 
function [trial_starts, trial_stops] = get_trial_windows(desired)
trial_starts = find(diff(any(desired, 2)) > 0);
trial_stops = find(diff(any(desired, 2)) < 0);
end
 
function task_results = get_task_results(control_rmse_int, experiment_rmse_int)
task_results.rmse.ctrl.int_a = control_rmse_int(1:2:end,1);
task_results.rmse.ctrl.int_b = control_rmse_int(2:2:end,1);
task_results.rmse.ctrl.xint_a = control_rmse_int(2:2:end,2);
task_results.rmse.ctrl.xint_b = control_rmse_int(1:2:end,2);
task_results.rmse.expl.int_a = experiment_rmse_int(1:2:end,1);
task_results.rmse.expl.int_b = experiment_rmse_int(2:2:end,1);
task_results.rmse.expl.xint_a = experiment_rmse_int(2:2:end,2);
task_results.rmse.expl.xint_b = experiment_rmse_int(1:2:end,2);
 
MODEL_SEED = [0.6, -0.2];
MODEL_TYPE = 'exp1';
rmse_len = length(control_rmse_int);
task_results.rmse_slopes.ctrl.int_a = fit((1:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.ctrl.int_a, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED);
task_results.rmse_slopes.ctrl.int_b = fit((2:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.ctrl.int_b, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED );
task_results.rmse_slopes.ctrl.xint_a = fit((2:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.ctrl.xint_a, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED );
task_results.rmse_slopes.ctrl.xint_b = fit((1:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.ctrl.xint_b, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED );
rmse_len = length(experiment_rmse_int);
task_results.rmse_slopes.expl.int_a = fit((1:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.expl.int_a, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED);
task_results.rmse_slopes.expl.int_b = fit((2:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.expl.int_b, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED);
task_results.rmse_slopes.expl.xint_a = fit((2:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.expl.xint_a, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED);
task_results.rmse_slopes.expl.xint_b = fit((1:2:rmse_len)', task_results.rmse.expl.xint_b, MODEL_TYPE, 'StartPoint', MODEL_SEED);
end
function plot_comparison(time_vals, desired, predicted, fig_title)
LINE_WIDTH = 1.75;
FIG_SIZE = [0, 0, 7, 5.25]*2.54; % in to cm
figure('Units','centimeters','Position', FIG_SIZE, 'Renderer','painters')
tlo = tiledlayout(2,1);
nexttile
if fig_title(1) == 'M'
[idx_start, ~] = get_trial_idxs(desired, 3);
[~, idx_stop] = get_trial_idxs(desired, 4);
else
[idx_start, ~] = get_trial_idxs(desired, 1);
[~, idx_stop] = get_trial_idxs(desired, 1);
end
plot(time_vals(idx_start:idx_stop), [predicted(idx_start:idx_stop,:), desired(idx_start:idx_stop,:)], LineWidth=LINE_WIDTH)
title("First Trial")
nexttile
[idx_start, ~] = get_trial_idxs(desired, 17);
[~, idx_stop] = get_trial_idxs(desired, 17);
plot(time_vals(idx_start:idx_stop), [predicted(idx_start:idx_stop,:), desired(idx_start:idx_stop,:)], LineWidth=LINE_WIDTH)
title("Last Trial")
title(tlo, fig_title)
end
